snippet.textDisplay: Coming from an immigrant Indian Sindhi family, I feel like I was denied privilege of knowing Sindh as a land, culture and community. I didn’t know „wali“ in Thar dialect means „wai hali“, I didn’t know Falsafo is philosophy. Each time they say „Khatte Aayi“ I feel that asanji Sindhi boli „Khatte aayi“ aahe. Sada jiye asanjo Sindh. Sada jiyan Sindh wara. Hats off to the creator!
snippet.textOriginal: Coming from an immigrant Indian Sindhi family, I feel like I was denied privilege of knowing Sindh as a land, culture and community.
